{"id":"lyr_6K645bu36ZO__MjI4Nw_0037","text":"從盲目愛到透明 就當我透明","structure":{"line_index":37,"char_count":12},"semantics":{"themes":["透明","關係"],"sentiment":"NEUTRAL","keywords":["盲目","透明"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,0,2,4,4,4,0,2,5,4,0],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["cung4","maang4","muk6","oi3","dou3","tau3","ming4","zau6","ngo5","tau3","ming4"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"從","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"盲目","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"愛到","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"透明","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"就","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"當","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"透明","pos":"ADJ"}],"syntax_notes":"「從盲目愛到透明」是關鍵轉折，表達愛意已變得毫無保留，甚至被視為理所當然。"},"source":{"title":"愛到透明","artists":["許廷鏗"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_2287","prev_line_id":"lyr_6K645bu36ZO__MjI4Nw_0036","next_line_id":"lyr_6K645bu36ZO__MjI4Nw_0038","paragraph_id":"para_08"}}
{"id":"lyr_6K645bu36ZO__MjI4Nw_0038","text":"其實我衷心高興 你忠於本性","structure":{"line_index":38,"char_count":12},"semantics":{"themes":["高興","本性"],"sentiment":"POSITIVE","keywords":["衷心","高興","忠於本性"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,2,5,3,3,3,3,5,3,3,9,4],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["kei4","sat6","ngo5","zung1","sam1","gou1","hing1","nei5","zung1","jyu1","bun2","sing3"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"其實","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"衷心","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"高興","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"忠於","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"本性","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"表達一種反諷式的高興，因為對方「忠於本性」而忽略自己，反而讓自己得以看清。"},"source":{"title":"愛到透明","artists":["許廷鏗"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_2287","prev_line_id":"lyr_6K645bu36ZO__MjI4Nw_0037","next_line_id":"lyr_6K645bu36ZO__MjI4Nw_0039","paragraph_id":"para_08"}}
